chat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1775026578188,"sessionId":"b04ea55b-b654-48be-a590-fdbedaab1866","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":44619,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/b04ea55b-b654-48be-a590-fdbedaab1866.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check for active sessions first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kkg76r7r4yrf_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775026578686}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775026586416}}
{"type":"message","id":"12aaf32b","parentId":"af61ed86","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:56:31.157Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session is the cron session itself. No actual user conversations in the last 5 minutes. I should proceed with the autonomous learning task.\n\nLet me search for latest news on enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services - topics relevant to 道简网络 (Daojian Network).","thinkingSignature":"eb5e2dd5fa866215656c16ead10626c0e8a1f3d924c41941710cc6e3d9a424dc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_cvsu420b5nfz_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":797,"output":107,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":44885,"cost":{"input":0.00023909999999999998,"output":0.0001284,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00168693}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775026586419}}
{"type":"message","id":"b5691f6e","parentId":"12aaf32b","timestamp":"2026-04-01T06:56:31.171Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_cvsu420b5nfz_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775026591166}}
